```plantuml
@startuml anvasquezre_sabiduria_asegurada_experiments

actor User
participant "Chainlit Front-end" as Frontend
participant "Langchain Agent" as Agent
participant "Qdrant Vector DB" as Qdrant
participant "Web Search API" as WebSearch
participant "Data Preloader" as Preloader
participant "S3 Bucket" as S3

User -> Frontend: Ask a question
Frontend -> Agent: Process question
Agent -> Qdrant: Search for policy info
Qdrant -> Agent: Return policy data
Agent -> WebSearch: Fetch related news
WebSearch -> Agent: Return news data
Agent -> Frontend: Provide answer
Frontend -> User: Display answer

== Data Pre-loading ==
Preloader -> S3: Download PDFs
S3 -> Preloader: Return PDFs
Preloader -> Preloader: Process PDFs
Preloader -> Qdrant: Store embeddings

@enduml
```